    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打造你的专属动物角色，甚至是一只小怪兽！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/af3008ab2601b5be96e138fd1f45cfc5.poster.avif?t=1772207704\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/af3008ab2601b5be96e138fd1f45cfc5.webm?t=1772207704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/af3008ab2601b5be96e138fd1f45cfc5.mp4?t=1772207704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个创意沙盒中，数百种选项尽在你的指尖，打造你的专属角色或复刻你熟悉的形象！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/85e4188c6fb3fc78bd653c5ac912dd28.poster.avif?t=1772207704\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/85e4188c6fb3fc78bd653c5ac912dd28.webm?t=1772207704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/85e4188c6fb3fc78bd653c5ac912dd28.mp4?t=1772207704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >捏出一只小可爱，再把它们扔来扔去。 看着它们奔跑、互动、嬉戏玩耍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超多角色，随心创造！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/8308e5d0df0b3adbbfde4a6108df9d94.poster.avif?t=1772207704\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/8308e5d0df0b3adbbfde4a6108df9d94.webm?t=1772207704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/8308e5d0df0b3adbbfde4a6108df9d94.mp4?t=1772207704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >万亿种组合！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/9467521484924cf38d1f1d0873448f8f.poster.avif?t=1772207704\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/9467521484924cf38d1f1d0873448f8f.webm?t=1772207704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/9467521484924cf38d1f1d0873448f8f.mp4?t=1772207704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >版本功能：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 轻松与好友分享你的创作</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 为你的小家伙穿上可爱的小衣服</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 还能把它们作为虚拟主播来用，麦克风检测就能自动对口型！</p>",
